    "nb_faq_drwekh": {
      "type": "nb-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_XFRb9B": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "q": "Will we coach in the 20-min call?",
            "a": "<p>The first call is a connection and fit check. We’ll get to know each other and explore where you are, and what you are looking for. If it feels right to both of us, we’ll book a longer deep-dive call to go into the details</p>",
            "open": true
          }
        },
        "item_YiD4KB": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "q": "What’s the difference between the 20-min call and the 60–90-min deep-dive?",
            "a": "<p>The deep-dive is where we go into the details. We’ll:</p><p>Define clear outcomes<br/>Surface patterns and what’s getting in the way<br/>Explain my coaching process</p><p>By the end, I will make an offer based on our conversation that would include investment, cadence, and logistics so you know exactly how it could look.<br/></p><p>You can say Yes or No to the offer at this point</p>",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_EbBYPA": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "q": "Do I have to decide on the call?",
            "a": "<p>I ask that you make a clear decision by the end of the second call, just so that it feels energetically clean. <br/><br/>Don't worry, No is always an acceptable answer. <br/><br/>And if there's still an appropriate reason to take more time to decide, then we can discuss that too. </p>",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "item_Cb8qic": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "q": "How do we meet—and what about time zones?",
            "a": "<p>Sessions are usually on Zoom. Calendly shows times in your local time zone automatically. If you need a different time or format, just mention it in the notes and we’ll make it work.</p>",
            "open": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "item_XFRb9B",
